{"tid":186745,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)家明上雪山 玩命快遞1-3","createTime":"2017-04-04T12:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T18:40:54.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b946078874da03260ec87cea5b9e99b1842d1151","tid":186745,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=0799ccf1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 按右上主頁可以睇返V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=91a68168\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.hiking.biji.co/static/upload/ex_52aea4ea3099d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.hiking.biji.co%2Fstatic%2Fupload%2Fex_52aea4ea3099d.jpg&h=8fce3007&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b2/The_Transporter_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb2%2FThe_Transporter_Poster.jpg&h=d7227631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/eb/The_Transporter_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Feb%2FThe_Transporter_2_poster.jpg&h=67aec41c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e5/Transporter_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe5%2FTransporter_3.jpg&h=558388bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.根據真人真事改編而成；一架載著橄欖球隊員的飛機在從烏拉圭飛往智利途中，意外墜毀於天寒地凍的安地斯山脈中，在經過猛烈撞擊後，僅剩下二十 多位倖存者，而圍繞著他們的只有散佈的飛機殘骸、罹難者屍體以及滿山的冰雪；在嚴苛的天候和環境下，飢寒交迫的他們為了生存，只得採取最不得已，也最駭人聽聞的方法：吃人肉..<br />\n<br />\n2.從特種部隊退休的法蘭克&middot;馬丁，在法國地中海樂園濱用「運輸者」的代號，駕駛BMW自營快遞生意，為各式各樣的委託人完成限時交易。對於工作，法蘭克有一套嚴格的規定：「不改變交易細節」、「不過問雙方姓名」、「不在乎快遞內容」..<br />\n<br />\n3.法蘭克&middot;馬丁（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）從法國南部搬遷至美國佛羅里達州邁阿密。出於人情，他暫時擔任有錢人家比令家族的司機。而由於傑佛遜（馬修&middot;摩丁飾）高姿態的政府工作需求，使得他與奧黛麗&middot;比令（琥珀&middot;瓦萊塔飾）的婚姻關係處於高度緊張狀態。法蘭克與比令夫妻就讀小學的兒子傑克（亨特&middot;克拉里飾）相處融洽，並每日駕駛著奧迪A8 W12載他上下學。[2]隨後，稍顯醉意的奧黛麗出現在法蘭克的家中，並且試圖勾引他，但法蘭克機靈地將她送回家..<br />\n<br />\n4.一家廢棄物回收商「ECO-CORP」，想要把回收來的有毒廢棄物運至烏克蘭丟棄，卻遭到烏克蘭環保部部長斷然拒絕，於是「ECO-CORP」命令槍手約拿.強生綁架了部長的愛女瓦倫蒂娜，想逼部長就範。強生認為自己運送肉票有危險，於是強迫了法蘭克接下了這個任務..<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7596d2533ecd24670eb1475838910dfb6cf1da6f","tid":186745,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c3a7667a56cf45843b391ed061b89ed4155ad9","tid":186745,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d71b67b72ea6b1cd42bf0d3356bd0a48c33584","tid":186745,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32593a4af897cb5b5f04a24fd1b7eac23d768648","tid":186745,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmo